high_descs: pick up the cup from the counter
turn left twice and walk to the counter. make a right and walk over to the stove
reach up and open the microwave. place the cup inside and turn it on.  open the microwave and take the cup out
Turn right twice and walk over towards the counter. turn left and walk over to the coffee maker
place the cup on the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: heat up a cup and put it in the coffee maker

high_descs: Move forward to stand in front of the sink with the coffee maker.
Pick the cup up from under the coffee maker.
Turn around and cross the room and turn right to face the microwave above the stove.
Put the cup in the microwave and shut the door and then open the door and take the mug out and shut the door.
Turn around and go left to stand at the counter in front of the coffee maker.
Put the cup under the coffee maker on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated cup under a coffee maker.

high_descs: Walk up to the coffee maker on the counter to the right of the sink.
Remove the coffee mug from under the spout of the coffee maker.
Turn around and walk across the kitchen to the counter top, then turn right and go to the microwave above the stove.
Put the coffee mug in the microwave and heat it up, then remove the coffee mug from the microwave.
Turn around and go past the refrigerator, to the coffee maker, on the counter, to your right.
Place the white coffee mug back under the spout of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm coffee mug on the coffee maker.
